'''硝酸钆'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为Gd(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它在[[核反应堆|核反应堆]]内用作[[中子毒物|中子毒物]]。<ref>{{cite book | title = DOE Fundamentals Handbook: Nuclear Physics and Reactor Theory | date = January 1993 | publisher = [[U.S._Department_of_Energy|U.S. Department of Energy]] | url = http://www.hss.energy.gov/NuclearSafety/techstds/standard/hdbk1019/h1019v2.pdf | accessdate = 2007-09-26 | pages = 31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080423194722/http://www.hss.energy.gov/NuclearSafety/techstds/standard/hdbk1019/h1019v2.pdf | archivedate = 2008-04-23 }}</ref>硝酸钆和其他[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]一样，是一种氧化剂。

==物理性质==
硝酸钆易溶于[[水|水]]。
